ed="T" n="0747a18"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0747a18"/><head><date from-iso="0923-05-18" key="j20583162063308" to-iso="0937-01-16">後唐</date><placeName key="PL000000002493">定州開元寺</placeName><persName key="A009888">貞辯</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0747a19"/><persName key="A009888">釋貞辯</persName>，<placeName key="PL000000002513">中山</placeName>人也。少知出塵，長誓修學，剋<ptr type="glossary" target="#g560"/><lb
ed="T" n="0747a20"/>苦之性，人不堪其憂。一志聽尋，暇則刺血<lb
ed="T" n="0747a21"/>書經，又鍼血畫立<persName key="A002803">觀自在</persName>像、<persName key="A001428">慈<roleName>氏</roleName></persName>像等。甞<lb
ed="T" n="0747a22"/>因行道困息，有二天女來相撓惱，<persName key="A009888">辯</persName>誓之<lb
ed="T" n="0747a23"/>曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A009888">我</ref>心匪石，<ref type="person" target="#A009888">吾</ref>以神呪被汝。」彼眾不容<lb
ed="T" n="0747a24"/>去。自此道勝，魔亦無蹤。<persName key="A009888">辯</persName>負笈抵<placeName key="PL000000003731">太原<lb
ed="T" n="0747a25"/>城</placeName>聽習，時<ref type="person" target="#A009920">中山王氏</ref>與<ref type="person" target="#A009891">後唐李氏</ref>封<ptr type="glossary" target="#g953"/>境相<lb
ed="T" n="0747a26"/>接，虞其覘間者，<placeName key="PL000000003731">并州城</placeName>內不容外僧。<persName key="A009888">辯</persName>由<lb
ed="T" n="0747a27"/>此驅出，遂於野外古塚間宿。會<persName key="A009891">武皇帝</persName><anchor xml:id="beg0747001"/>畋<anchor xml:id="end0747001"/><lb
ed="T" n="0747a28"/>遊，塚在圍場中。<persName key="A009888">辯</persName>固不知，方將入城赴<lb
ed="T" n="0747a29"/>講，見旌旗騎卒，縮身還入穴中。<persName key="A009891">武皇</persName>疑，令<pb ed="T" n="0747b" xml:id="T50.2061.0747b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0747b01"/>擒見，問其故，遂驗塚中，敷草座，案、硯、疏、鈔<lb
ed="T" n="0747b02"/>羅布，遂命入府供養。時<persName key="A000787">曹太后</persName>深加仰重，<lb
ed="T" n="0747b03"/><persName key="A009888">辯</persName>訴於<ref type="person" target="#A000787">太后</ref>曰：「止以學法為懷，久在王<lb
ed="T" n="0747b04"/>宮不樂，如梏械<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1069"/>耳。」<persName key="A009891">武皇</persName>縱其自由，乃成其<lb
ed="T" n="0747b05"/>業。洎<persName key="A009920">王處直</persName>平，乃歸<placeName key="PL000000002511">中山</placeName>講訓，補故伽藍，<lb
ed="T" n="0747b06"/>無不諧願。有<persName key="A000788">婦人陳<roleName>氏</roleName></persName>布髮掩地，請<persName key="A009888">辯</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0747b07"/>蹈之。撰《上生經鈔》，為學者所貴，時號《辯<lb
ed="T" n="0747b08"/>鈔》者是。後終于<ref type="place" target="#PL000000002493">此寺</ref>焉。</p>
